    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the culture of the modern nation of Portugal, or in general to the cultures that have occupied the same area in the western part of the Iberian Peninsula.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
